SHEPARD et al., Respondents, v. SQUIRE et al., Appellants. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fifth Department. March 27, 1894.) Action by Floyd C. Shepard and others against Watson G. Squire and another.

Argued before DWIGHT, P. X, and LEWIS, HAIGHT, and BRADLEY, JJ.

No opinion. Order denying motion to change place of trial appealed from reversed, with disbursements to the appellants. •
